flowchart TD
  A[JSONL Manifest] --> B[VoiceCloneManifestDataset]
  B -->|ref_wav @16k| C[WeSpeakerSV Frozen]
  B -->|target_wav @24k| TGT[Target waveform]
  B -->|text/lang -> phonemes -> input_ids| TOK[Token IDs]

  C -->|frame_features| D[SegmentGST]
  C -->|pooled_embedding ref| EREF[Ref speaker embedding]

  D -->|ref_s style vector 256d| K[Kokoro KModel]
  TOK --> K
  K -->|pred_wav @24k| PRED[Pred waveform]

  PRED --> MEL[MelReconstructionLoss]
  TGT --> MEL

  PRED --> MELSV[speaker_input_mel_from_waveform]
  MELSV --> C2[WeSpeakerSV Frozen]
  C2 -->|pooled_embedding gen| EGEN[Gen speaker embedding]
  EREF --> SPK[speaker_cosine_loss]
  EGEN --> SPK

  TGT --> DISC[HiFiGAN MPD+MSD Discriminator]
  PRED -->|detach for D-step| DISC
  DISC --> DLOSS[discriminator_loss_lsgan]

  PRED --> DISC2[Discriminator for G-step]
  DISC2 --> GADV[generator_loss_lsgan]
  DISC2 --> FM[feature_matching_loss vs real features]

  MEL --> SUM[Generator total loss]
  SPK --> SUM
  GADV --> SUM
  FM --> SUM

  SUM --> OPTG[AdamW Generator]
  DLOSS --> OPTD[AdamW Discriminator]
